value: Senegal south to Bornu and eastward to central Kordofan; also occurs in the Turkwel country and in the sandy areas of Uganda and northern Kenya Colony.

value: Resident and intra-African migrant, grassland and thorn scrub: Sahel zone N Senegal - E Sudan; S Ethiopia and parts of Kenya.
Discontinuously distributed sahel of sub-Saharan Africa

Savanna, particularly of Acacia and Chrysopogon and grasslands habitats where grass cover exceeds 25%.In some areas of W Africa favours sandy localities, often without surface water;to 200m, usually below 1200m in E Africa
